// Yazelix-specific overrides
//
// Applied at the merged config.kdl layer for static snippets that should not
// depend on layout-local loading behavior.
// Yazelix-owned pane-orchestrator action binds are rendered from
// settings.jsonc zellij.keybindings by rust_core/yazelix_core/src/zellij_materialization.rs.
// Curated native Zellij key policy is rendered from
// settings.jsonc zellij.native_keybindings.
